Fmoad Cailin
============

Partial reimplementation of FMOD with OpenAL.

Once a great stronghold, now much of it stands in ruins.

Similar project: https://github.com/moon-chilled/openfmod

What You Need
-------------

* openal
* vorbisfile

How To Use
----------

Same preparation as with [openfmod](https://github.com/moon-chilled/openfmod):

- Drop file `libfmodstudio.so` in the game's directory. Make sure the dllmap file(s) for the game point for all {,lib}fmod{,studio} to this file.

Native Bank Loading
-------------------

fmoad-cailin can now load FMOD banks natively without external tools.

When `FMOD_Studio_System_LoadBankFile` is called:

1. It first looks for a JSON manifest (`bankname.json`) alongside the `.bank` file.
   If found, it uses the manifest for event metadata (existing behavior).

2. If no JSON manifest is found, it parses the `.bank` file directly:
   - Locates the embedded FSB5 audio data
   - Extracts all samples as OGG files into `bankname.banko/`
   - Creates synthetic event entries for each sample

This eliminates the need for `fsb-extract-dumb` and `python-fsb5`.

How to Build
------------

```
$ make
```

And Then?
----------

Drop file `libfmodstudio.so` in the game's directory. Make sure the dllmap file(s) for the game point for all {,lib}fmod{,studio} to this file.

What Works
----------

* Celeste (partially; being tested at the moment)

Other games remain to be seen...

Debugging
---------

In order to get more verbose output, set the `FMOAD_LOGLEVEL` environment variable to 1 (or greater for more verbosity).

